hidden entirely by defining \fBOPENSSL_API_COMPAT\fR with a suitable version value,
see \fBopenssl_user_macros\fR\|(7):
.PP
.Vb 1
\& void BF_set_key(BF_KEY *key, int len, const unsigned char *data);
\&
